snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Environments
snippet.description: Minecraft Dungeons is a new action-adventure game set in the Minecraft Universe. In this episode you’ll get a preview of the different levels, find out how we create them, and discover how plot affects the environment! https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/about-dungeons
